    "name": "不思议迷宫",
    "steam_appid": 3112010,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是的你没看错，这是不思议迷宫！...的Steam畅玩版，我们想将带给过大家的纯粹快乐延续下去，所以决定将不思议<strong>免费上架</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在Steam版本中，仅<strong>保留了大家最喜欢的迷宫玩法</strong>，去掉了天空、外域和一些放置玩法；去掉了体力等限制条件；去掉了黄金之罐等付费内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >希望不思议迷宫可以再次让大家获得快乐、重温快乐，冈布奥们会一直在，<strong>再出发，依然不思议</strong>！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>由于该版本是为了延续游戏纯粹的快乐而制作的，且免费上架纯属为爱发电，我们尚未对此版本进行更多的适配，只进行了最基本的移植，比如还没有做横屏适配，感谢大家的理解，就请先将就玩一下吧！</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>友情提示：Steam版本为独立版本，与其他平台数据不可互通。</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款独具特色的<strong>Roguelike迷宫探险游戏</strong>，带领你的冈布奥开启一场充满惊喜和挑战的冒险吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/caa74db4ef0c7aa30de0dc2de6593148.avif?t=1764738164\" width=658 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每一层都是随机生成的迷宫里，每一个石板下都藏着未知的东西，可能是可怕的怪物，可能是救命的血瓶，可能是一个神秘的洞窟，也可能是...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/c98544f4027c820adb69a75aa3ccc8d0.poster.avif?t=1764738164\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/c98544f4027c820adb69a75aa3ccc8d0.webm?t=1764738164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/c98544f4027c820adb69a75aa3ccc8d0.mp4?t=1764738164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/342f773c2c793d7324dc77d5cddb2ffe.poster.avif?t=1764738164\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/342f773c2c793d7324dc77d5cddb2ffe.webm?t=1764738164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/342f773c2c793d7324dc77d5cddb2ffe.mp4?t=1764738164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/9c54a20b4872b07bc3090a4bf8665e6e.avif?t=1764738164\" width=658 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个主题迷宫都有独特的玩法，有的可以提交果子给猴子让它帮你战斗、有的在祭坛里放入不同的水晶组合触发不同的效果、有的甚至可以跟神灯许愿...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/ecd38bc93c98d1e7086c89eb7c1ca8eb.poster.avif?t=1764738164\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/ecd38bc93c98d1e7086c89eb7c1ca8eb.webm?t=1764738164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/ecd38bc93c98d1e7086c89eb7c1ca8eb.mp4?t=1764738164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/5f269b233992528d63a9b7fa9953dde8.poster.avif?t=1764738164\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/5f269b233992528d63a9b7fa9953dde8.webm?t=1764738164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/5f269b233992528d63a9b7fa9953dde8.mp4?t=1764738164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/a16980415978ca3931db7a6ba746cdbf.avif?t=1764738164\" width=658 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在探索迷宫的过程中，你将有机会遇到上百种精彩的彩蛋，让你的旅程永远充满惊喜与期待，如果你有幸集齐了7颗龙珠召唤神龙，你会许愿变有钱，还是获得无尽的生命？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/ff292ea6594ff373e773961d3d04969b.poster.avif?t=1764738164\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/ff292ea6594ff373e773961d3d04969b.webm?t=1764738164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/ff292ea6594ff373e773961d3d04969b.mp4?t=1764738164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/ded895b9bb21fcf87a1732b6c725dccb.poster.avif?t=1764738164\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/ded895b9bb21fcf87a1732b6c725dccb.webm?t=1764738164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/ded895b9bb21fcf87a1732b6c725dccb.mp4?t=1764738164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/41b5d7ebb1fcebac1e61ee759960f1d2.avif?t=1764738164\" width=658 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >上百个技能各异的冈布奥，多种免费获取途径，冈布奥们之间还有灵魂链接，进入迷宫后可以拥有3个冈布奥的专属技能！噢对了，创作人还把自己做成了“冈布猴”放进了游戏里...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/496322bc6e9575f5a478a19b106df521.poster.avif?t=1764738164\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/496322bc6e9575f5a478a19b106df521.webm?t=1764738164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/496322bc6e9575f5a478a19b106df521.mp4?t=1764738164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/685d33f7ed0655a72de595d58e6677c4.poster.avif?t=1764738164\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/685d33f7ed0655a72de595d58e6677c4.webm?t=1764738164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/685d33f7ed0655a72de595d58e6677c4.mp4?t=1764738164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/f5ebb1b5dbe7a5548313dcb2ab5b3daf.avif?t=1764738164\" width=658 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个迷宫都有专属的强大BOSS，有的能反弹攻击，有的免疫某些魔法，有的在你以为快要战胜的时候会突然变换形态... 动用你强大的脑力，去一个个战胜他们吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/6171e1ebf0efbba5636f692bf41d2abe.poster.avif?t=1764738164\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/6171e1ebf0efbba5636f692bf41d2abe.webm?t=1764738164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/6171e1ebf0efbba5636f692bf41d2abe.mp4?t=1764738164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/372936b427510d6812255cdfba9ae3d9.poster.avif?t=1764738164\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/372936b427510d6812255cdfba9ae3d9.webm?t=1764738164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/372936b427510d6812255cdfba9ae3d9.mp4?t=1764738164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/4780c2988741dc8fb39c608a13b1f3de.avif?t=1764738164\" width=658 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个通往千年之后的时空裂缝，让这块充满了冒险回忆的大陆显得既陌生又熟悉，那棵鏖战了多回合的战争古树都已枯萎... 遗落圣坛和德古拉城堡又会有什么变化呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/2ea4a3bde305da7c7a9a5f460c596d2d.poster.avif?t=1764738164\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/2ea4a3bde305da7c7a9a5f460c596d2d.webm?t=1764738164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/2ea4a3bde305da7c7a9a5f460c596d2d.mp4?t=1764738164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/509af6b22d7c080750696a7607dee84d.poster.avif?t=1764738164\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/509af6b22d7c080750696a7607dee84d.webm?t=1764738164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112010/extras/509af6b22d7c080750696a7607dee84d.mp4?t=1764738164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_pa